flowchart LR
  %% Slices
  GOV[Governance Slice<br/>Rules + Taxonomy]
  CAL[Calendar Slice<br/>Projects + Funding Demands + Execution]
  SPN[Sponsors Slice<br/>Prospects + Pledges + Donation Records]
  FIN[Finance Slice<br/>Book of Record (GL) + Reserves + Encumbrances]
  LGR[Ledger Slice<br/>Append-only Events (no PII)]

  %% Key objects (cheap labels)
  DEM[(Funding Demand<br/>funding_demand_ulid)]
  INT[(Funding Intent<br/>pledge/prospect)]
  INC[(Income Receipt<br/>deposit/received)]
  RSV[(Reserve<br/>locked funds)]
  ENC[(Encumbrance<br/>commitment)]
  EXP[(Expense<br/>spend)]

  %% Demand generation + publish
  CAL -->|create/update| DEM
  GOV -->|taxonomy + controls (read-only)| CAL
  CAL -->|publish demand (read-only query)| SPN

  %% Intent + receipt of funds
  SPN -->|record pledge/prospect| INT
  SPN -->|donation received → post_income(...)| FIN
  INC --> FIN
  SPN -->|links to demand| DEM

  %% Reserves for fundraising / accumulation
  FIN -->|auto reserve if designated| RSV
  RSV -->|references| DEM

  %% Execution: approvals → encumber → spend
  CAL -->|preview/approve rules (read-only)| GOV
  CAL -->|encumber_funds(..., decision_ref)| FIN
  FIN --> ENC
  ENC -->|references| DEM

  CAL -->|post_expense(..., encumbrance_ulid)| FIN
  FIN --> EXP
  EXP -->|references| DEM

  %% Ledger events (conceptual)
  CAL -.->|events| LGR
  SPN -.->|events| LGR
  FIN -.->|events| LGR
  GOV -.->|events| LGR
